{"tid":603023,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點食到女/溝到仔,你問,大家答","createTime":"2018-03-23T11:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T04:02:35.000Z","uid":175347,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9f34340e9d46be60c090241c1bcacf1205670ece","tid":603023,"uid":175347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:17:18.000Z","msg":"上次開左個po幾熱烈,一齊再交流下傾下計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/590934/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/590934/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n由上年諗住識下女仔點知第1個就主動問會唔會一齊,唔既SP都OK. 之後就上左食女之路,開始計住食左幾多,等. 到新年前3X個到. happy sharing分享下心得<br />\n<br />\n另外有幾個ADD左我tg(其實爸打都ADD得).其實絲打溝仔都會有煩惱嫁,一齊幫下佢地<br />\n<br />\n以下係上個po熱門問題(hottest post first)<br />\n<br />\n1. 有冇食過處<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無。有都唔敢，過唔到自己果關。要食得有道德</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 樓上班柒頭 人生要幾失敗先要用 食咗幾多條女 嚟拎成就感<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;食得兩個喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &ldquo; 睇見都想嘔 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果換轉係絲打開po 話俾幾多個人上過 點點點 <br />\n肯定祖宗十八代都俾人掘出嚟屌</span><br />\n<br />\n呸<br />\n<br />\n3.食唔到既有幾多條？？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可能都有好多，但傾幾句就知佢想找男友定玩</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 年齡range?<br />\n多數扑一次定長期sp<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">18-28 <br />\n可長期但小弟就五次內就悶</span><br />\n身材如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇試過除bra 見到aa想即走<br />\n試過假E奶，硬到hihi,打下碟後叫佢幫我唅出來就算..</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 驗左愛滋未? 捐血免費有得驗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有驚過，有期夏天發燒久病不癒。always condom on</span><br />\n<br />\n6.有咩絕招 出完99.9%一定食到？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無<br />\n</span><br />\n7. 巴打有咩過人之處令你食到咁多女?<br />\n或者講下你有d咩係令到女冧你？又有咩缺乏？<br />\n無樣無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">信心，態度更重要</span><br />\n<br />\n8.點樣多啲match<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">睇你個profile點build? 一張運動順手show muscle?一張同媽咪合照但玩味既，一張西裝？一張同幾個女仔fd合照？</span><br />\n<br />\n9.#49<br />\n強迫症（治療中）<br />\n&bull;<br />\n10 日前<br />\n點識<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">App, 唔係玩幾日就有。但慢慢你會知點樣&ldquo;decorate&rdquo;自己個profile,同邊d位入得<br />\nBar, club<br />\n用咩APP？有冇推薦<br />\n其實唔關app事，關人事，黎黎去去咪skout tinder.<br />\nTinder我覺得難d,不過食得太多有時要停下，有種空虛感覺</span><br />\n<br />\n10.樓主用乜野PROFILE PIC?<br />\n應該難d screenshot 你看..<br />\n乜類型...運動？泊埋寵物到？？之類<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都可以，但如運動，揀surfing, skating, x game, polo，等唔多人玩既。寵物一樣，</span><br />\n夾band 時被影果d相得唔得？<br />\n揸住支他果d？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">影得型都ok。我都有彈不過無用</span><br />\n樂器追女冇用？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲係𡃁仔咩</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝絲打借出J圖一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/191502_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F191502_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg&h=1b32f9fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">上個post我真係出於好心既..不過算啦我自己on9,不過點都好我都會自己搵方法捐</span>"},{"pid":"5ec41e1c88ee2137920afc45c34afd2af0a7d0a4","tid":603023,"uid":18568,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n廢柴扮食女高手<br />\n仲想借斷腳媽賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af2fec50d405917bf93738f4396a8084a2a6091","tid":603023,"uid":175347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ec41e1c88ee2137920afc45c34afd2af0a7d0a4","tid":603023,"uid":18568,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n廢柴扮食女高手<br />\n仲想借斷腳媽賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"大家答咋！<br />\n嗯，我錯了。無跟進新聞。咁佢話有需要我自己幫吧。謝謝"},{"pid":"82945c4